			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">When using the dataset for Life Cycle Assessment (LCA) calculations of products or services involving shale gas, ensure that the geographical scope is consistent with the region from which the data was sourced, namely Sichuan and Chongqing. Attention should be paid to the impact assessment phase to consider the local environmental impact categories. Additionally, users should account for technological advancements in extraction techniques and potential variations in data due to policy changes or natural resource availability when applying this dataset.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">在使用该数据集进行涉及页岩气的产品或服务的生命周期评估(LCA)计算时，应确保地理范围与数据来源地区相符，即四川和重庆地区。在影响评估阶段应注重考虑当地环境影响类别。此外，用户在应用此数据集时，应考虑采取技术进步提高页岩气抽取技术，并注意政策变化或自然资源可用性可能导致数据的变动。</useAdviceForDataSet>
		</dataSourcesTreatmentAndRepresentativeness>
